410
00:26:10,120 --> 00:26:11,120
Meng Meng, I won't do that.

411
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:21,920
You were hiding in the dark under
the staircase. Were you frightened?

412
00:26:25,280 --> 00:26:26,360
Don't be afraid.

413
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:27,840
I'm here.

414
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,240
I will protect you from now on.

415
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,720
Meng Meng.

416
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:42,240
You're not frightened of me, are you?

417
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:47,920
Well...

418
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,240
Then you draw first.

419
00:27:04,840 --> 00:27:05,840
Meng Meng.

420
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,400
I sit here.

421
00:27:13,017 --> 00:27:14,077
Don't be afraid.

422
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,480
I'm here to watch you draw.

423
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,120
I'll be with you.

424
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:19,840
You may draw it.

425
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,160
You may draw it.

426
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:03,760
That's our son,

427
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:05,720
