00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:49,040
this is a good thing.

555
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:51,200
What if we can't live to be a hundred?

556
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,440
As you can see,

557
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,880
Zhang Zhong Jing

558
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:01,160
didn't live a long life.

559
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,480
He lived into his sixties.

560
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:04,200
But in my opinion,

561
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,480
he had longevity.

562
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:08,880
A man's longevity

563
00:36:09,520 --> 00:36:10,557
doesn't depend on

564
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:12,960
the actual time he lives.

565
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:18,160
One's real longevity
is about his mind and character.

566
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:20,157
Many people still remember him,

567
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:21,640
and commemorate him now,

568
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,440
it means he's not dead.

569
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:28,597
Yang, I don't think

570
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:30,200
you're alone.

571
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:33,680
Your family is watching you from heaven.

572
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:40,840
If they see
you can't afford to let go of this,

573
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,360
they won't rest in peace.

574
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:46,360
If I were your mother,

575
00:36:46,520 --> 00:36:48,240
seeing how tangled

576
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,680
your daily life is,

577
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,040
I wouldn't feel at ease.

578
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:05,680
Here's something for you.

579
00:37:08,680 --> 00:37:09,680
Money box.

580
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:15,840
Why is this full?

581
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:18,120
Money box

582
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,880
will then be shattered
once the money is stuffed.

583
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,040
This is the process of accumulation.

584
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:24,520
It's a

585
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,117
highly motivating

586
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,557
and exciting process.

587
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:28,680
But on the other hand,

588
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,480
if it's full,

589
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,200
it never escapes

590
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:34,720
from being shattered.

591
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:37,960
That's how life is.

592
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:40,920
You only focus to accumulate,

593
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,960
but you don't evacuate

594
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,280
and apply.

595
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:46,680
It's sure to be shattered.

596
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:50,040
There is an in and an out,

597
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,880
a Yin and a Yang, that's the way.

598
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:56,160
Hence, I'm giving it to you.

599
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:58,680
It's also an assignment for you.

600
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:12,360
This is all you've got in it.

601
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,680
You have to know

602
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:18,720
how to apply it.

603
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,520
If one day

604
00:38:21,520 --> 00:38:24,240
you can take
the initiative to help others,

605
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:26,360
I'll take out one yuan

606
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:27,960
from this money box.

607
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:32,200
When it's empty,

608
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,480
I will take you as my disciple.

609
00:38:51,600 --> 00:38:52,600
-Jian Xi.
-Ms Song.

610
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:57,120
Has your appetite improved recently?

611
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:58,920
Much better.

612
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:01,360
The medicine is quite good, isn't it?

613
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
That's great.

614
00:39:03,200 --> 00:39:04,437
Then you'll have to
continue taking the medication

615
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:06,600
we prescribed to you for some time.

616
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:10,840
Zhu Xia.

617
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:13,600
-Are you still looking for a tile?
-Yes.

618
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:18,360
There's a lot of information out there,
but it's unreliable.

619
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:22,600
We will soon be providing free
consultations in the suburbs.

620
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:26,000
The possibility of obtaining

621
00:39:27,280 --> 00:39:29,877
centuries-old tiles

622
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:31,200
in remote mountain areas is greater.

623
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,277
I'll keep an eye out for you then.

624
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,680
Okay, thank you, Ms Song.

625
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,280
You're welcome.

626
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,080
Get more exposure to the sunlight.

627
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:41,880
Let's go ahead.

628
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:53,640
Hello.

629
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,960
I'd like to rent a
two-bedroom apartment.

630
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:59,160
Preferably with lift access
and close to the metro.

631
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,160
Budget...

632
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,680
My budget is around 6,000 yuan.

633
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:03,920
The sooner, the better.

634
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:08,920
Yes, I am available to view houses
after work on weekdays.

635
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:11,600
Okay.

636
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,960
Thank you.

637
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:18,240
Are you really
going to move out with Meng Meng?

638
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:21,560
I am up against my mum this time.

639
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,000
That's not right.

640
00:40:24,520 --> 00:40:26,960
You're against your mum
because of Meng Meng.

641
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:29,400
Two years later, you don't
even know where Meng Meng is.

642
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:32,480
You still have to pass on
your family's legacy.

643
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:34,960
Are you going to leave your
parents and grandparents behind?

644
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,360
It won't happen.

645
00:40:39,040 --> 00:40:40,477
You haven't got a clue about my mum.

646
00:40:40,560 --> 00:40:41,760
She will never fall out with me.

647
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:43,240
After a while,

648
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:45,440
this problem will be solved.

649
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:54,066
Have you fallen in love with Meng Meng?

650
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:56,020
What a load of nonsense.

